title: Walt Disney's Toby Tyler
description: OUR COPY HAS THE SAME COVER AS STOCK PHOTO SHOWN. TAPING OVER SPINE INTO FRONT AND BACK COVERS. SCUFFING AND WEAR ON CORNERS AND EDGES OF BOARDS. BINDING RELEASING INSIDE BOTH COVERS. PAGES INTACT AND SHOW AGE RELATED TANNING WITH SOME DISCOLORATION. MUSTY ODOR.
author: Dorothea J. Snow
